OL,6,FOffice workers flocked to transport
OL,7,Fhubs as demand for workspaces closer
OL,8,Fto home ballooned in 2025, data shows.
OL,10,FProfessionals are increasingly
OL,11,Fshifting away from the traditional
OL,12,Fdaily commute in favour of more
OL,13,Fconvenient working arrangements,
OL,14,Faccording to one of the world's
OL,15,Fbiggest workspace firms.
OL,17,FData from International Workplace
OL,18,FGroup (IWG) shows an average 33% rise
OL,19,Fin visits to transport-linked
OL,20,Flocations in 2025, compared with the
OL,21,Fprevious year
