OL,3,COffice workers flocked to travel hubs
OL,4,Ccloser to home in 2025, data shows
OL,6,FThis spike was most prominent within
OL,7,Fsome of the UK's busiest motorway
OL,8,Fcorridors, including the M25, M4, M3
OL,9,Fand M5.
OL,11,FThe strongest growth was recorded in
OL,12,FBrentwood, Essex, which is located
OL,13,Fclose to the M25 and nearby service-
OL,14,Fstation traffic, where visits to
OL,15,Foffices soared by 50% year-on-year.
OL,17,FVisits rose by 37% in Hatfield,
OL,18,FHertfordshire, while Frimley and Fleet
OL,19,Falong the M3 corridor recorded
OL,20,Fincreases of 35% and 30% respectively.
