OL,4,Ccloser to home in 2025, data shows
OL,6,FThe data also showed spikes in
OL,7,Fattendance around rail-connected
OL,8,Flocations in major cities including
OL,9,FLondon Blackfriars, where footfall
OL,10,Frocketed 139%.
OL,12,FFlexible office locations close to
OL,13,Fmajor stations in Leeds, Birmingham,
OL,14,FEdinburgh and Liverpool rose by up to
OL,15,F47%, as professionals sought out
OL,16,Fplaces to work between meetings or
OL,17,Fchose to commute part-time into city
OL,18,Fcentres, the workspace group found.
