OL,3,COffice workers flocked to travel hubs
OL,4,Ccloser to home in 2025, data shows
OL,6,FIWG's founder and chief executive Mark
OL,7,FDixon said: "Companies of all sizes
OL,8,Fare embracing more flexible ways of
OL,9,Fworking for the long-term, empowering
OL,10,Ftheir people to work from locations
OL,11,Fthat are most convenient to them and
OL,12,Ftheir lifestyles and at the same time
OL,13,Fboosting company productivity.
OL,15,F"As a result, we're seeing a
OL,16,Ffundamental shift in the geography of
OL,17,Fwork, with demand moving towards more
OL,18,Flocal and accessible locations
OL,19,Fincluding travel hubs.
